This token is populated from JWT handler and proper then httpRequest is created with this. And then passed to further filters in the chain.
Hence even if Spnego comes later, this wont be a pblm. Infact this code is present in from long time and works well with KNOX SSO and UI1. This Jira extends same to UI2.

